text: Abryna rubeta is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Francis Polkinghorne Pascoe in 1864. It is known from Borneo and Malaysia.BioLib.cz - Abryna rubeta. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Pteropliini Category:Beetles described in 1864
title: Abryna rubeta
